You find the copykey!!!! It falls on the floor...
> take copykey

> take copykey

You decide to take the copykey.

You feel the imaginary noises coming closer and closer together. How to get out?!

> use copykey on door

> use copykey on door

You put the copykey in the lock victoriously!
.
.
