But nothing happens! You burst into tears!!!!
> knock on door

> knock on door

Of course!

"...Knock and the door will be opened to you. For everyone who knocks, the door will be opened..."

Maybe the problem wasn't my lack of trying, but my lack of faith all along...

You knock, hear the lock clicking, and see the door opening.

On the other side is Jesus welcoming you in his embrace!

THE END!

CONGRATULATIONS ON COMPLETING THE GAME!!!
